settings.title: planet friendly
settings.content: The carbon footprint of insects is 30 times smaller per kg than that of a cow. This means that by serving Gutsy, which contains insects as a protein source, you and your dog have the chance to reduce your own carbon footprint too.

settings.content: To keep our pawprint as small as possible, we exclusively choose local products. All of the ingredients of Gutsy are produced within a radius of 100 miles of XXX.

settings.headline: HYPOALLERGENIC
settings.paragraph: Our kibble is hypoallergenic and therefore perfect for dogs with sensitive stomachs. Allergic reactions are a thing of the past, you can ask our very own Otis!

settings.paragraph: Not all proteins are easy to digest. That’s where Gutsy makes the difference. We only use high-quality and easy digestible proteins in our dog food.
